Barroso Says EFSF Should Be Maximized, ESM Launch Accelerated

-- B y   P a t r i c k   H e n r y
-- 
2011-10-12T13:37:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/barroso-says-efsf-should-be-maximized-esm-launch-accelerated.html
European Commission President  Jose
Barroso  said the European Union must “maximize” the capacity
of the temporary European Financial Stability Facility and
accelerate the launch of the permanent European Stability
Mechanism, “preferably” to mid-2012. He spoke to the European
Parliament in Brussels today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Patrick Henry at 
 phenry8@bloomberg.net  